<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">



	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<title>Tobi's Projects | Home</title>
		<!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" /> -->
		<link href="style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />

	</head>

	<body>

		<nav>
			<h1>Tobi's Projects</h1>
			<ul>
				{% for project in projects %}
				<li>
					<a href="#{{ project.name|replace({' ': '-'})|lower }}" >
						{{ project.name }}
					</a>
				</li>
				{% endfor %}
			</ul>
		</nav>

		<section class="main col uno">
			{% for project in projects %}
				<article id="{{ project.id }}">
					<header>
						<h1 id="{{ project.name|replace({' ':'-'})|lower }}">
							{{ project.name }}
						</h1>
					</header>

					<a target="_BLANK" href="{{ project.url }}">
						<img style="width:100%;" src="{{ project.covers.original }}">
					</a>

					<footer>
						<p style="text-align:right">{{ project.owners[0].occupation }} |
						{{ project.owners[0].city }}, {{ project.owners[0].country }}</p>
					</footer>
				</article>
			{% endfor %}
		</section>

		<aside class="side col dos">
			<h2>About section</h2>
			<p>Donec eu libero sit amet quam egestas semper. Aenean ultricies mi vitae est. Mauris placerat eleifend leo.</p>
		</aside>

		<footer class="footer row" >
			<p>Â© 2016 el Tob | </p>
		</footer>

	</body>
</html>